summary: Smoothed, redone and about 20 years younger than the default one.
descriptionHtml:
Younger Bretons

Update: Now with male Bretons as an optional file!
_______________________________

For all the people who always wanted to play a female Breton, but didn\'t because they\'re all old by default.

Based on the \"Younger Characters\" Mod by Limbek, heavily edited with his permission.

- Completely smoothed out
- Even less wrinkles (see neck for example)

Install:

Unrar (WinRar, 7zip, use whatever you prefer) and move the Data folder to your Skyrim folder.

Uninstall:

Remove \"femalehead_msn.dds\" in \\Data\\textures\\actors\\character\\bretonfemale\\
_______________________________

Recommended additions:

Detailed Faces V2: http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=26
Detailed Lips: http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=689
High Quality Eyes (Darker & Desaturated): http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=498
Telthalions Finer Hair: http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2207

_________

Savegame with that female character:
http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2563

_________
